snippet.title: Season 4: The Heart of the Dragon Official Trailer | Clashes unfold Sept 12, 2025 | Marvel Rivals
snippet.description:
üêâ Marvel Rivals Season 4: Heart of the Dragon begins on September 12th

The Timestream Entanglement has drawn the Seven Capitals together, forming the Heart of Heaven. After Knull‚Äôs fall, Hela is imprisoned in the An'Hay-Zhidi, where Dizang‚ÄîDevil of the Eighth City‚Äîdares her to atone for her sins. But Angela will not forgive her betrayal. She arrives in the Heart of Heaven demanding Hela be handed over, yet its guardian refuses to surrender someone under his protection. Justice will be served and a debt will be paid.

But while they fight, an even greater danger stirs. Doctor Doom seeks to steal the Chronal Chi of the slumbering dragon Shou-Lao, threatening to unravel the fate of the Heavens themselves.

Expanding upon the world created by Danny Boyle and Alex Garland in 28 Years Later but turning that world on its head - Nia DaCosta directs 28 Years Later: The Bone Temple. In a continuation of the epic story, Dr. Kelson (Ralph Fiennes) finds himself in a shocking new relationship - with consequences that could change the world as they know it - and Spike's (Alfie Williams) encounter with Jimmy Crystal (Jack O'Connell) becomes a nightmare he can't escape. In the world of The Bone Temple, the infected are no longer the greatest threat to survival - the inhumanity of the survivors can be stranger and more terrifying.

The action includes everything from high-speed car chases to on-foot stealth sequences and shootouts. snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle  |  VS VISUAL 2 TRAILER
snippet.description:
The Paths We've Chosen To Take ‚ö°
Experience Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle on the big screen starting September 12 in the United States and Canada! Tickets are on sale now!

üéüÔ∏è BUY TICKETS NOW: https://www.demonslayer-movie.com/tickets/

Official Website: https://demonslayer-anime.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/demonslayer.anime/
X: https://x.com/demonslayerusa

About Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle:
Tanjiro Kamado ‚Äì a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon. 

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps‚Äô highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.
The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons‚Äô stronghold ‚Äì the Infinity Castle. 

And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Movie Musicals 123: Jurassic World Rebirth The Musical
Zora Bennett & Henry Loomis are hired by pharmaceutical executive Martin Krebs to get some dino samples to cure heart disease, but there's a catch: they must sing and dance along with the dinosaurs such as Spinosaurus, Mosasaurus, Quetzalcoatlus, T-Rex, Distortus-Rex, Mutadons, and an Aquilops named Dolores. Mercs Bobby Atwater, Nina, and Duncan are coaxed into it along with the unfortunate family Delgado family who are in the wrong place at the wrong time. All in a hard day's work.

‚ñ∫Animation, Lyrics, Song, & Vocals: Logan Hugueny-Clark @lhugueny 
‚ñ∫Co-Producer & Vocals: Whitney Di Stefano @TheVoiceTree 
‚ñ∫Special Guest Rapper: James Beavers @AGamingBeaver 
‚ñ∫Thanks to Jurassic World: @jurassicworld 

LYRICS
(Verse)
Dinosaurs are dying in the streets,
Pharma exec wants to hire me.
I know he‚Äôs got deep pockets,
Leave faster than a rocket.
Our mission‚Äôs underway and,
Nobody can stop it.
Boat full of mercenaries,
To fill the dinos‚Äô bellies.
Can we extract their DNA?

(Pre-chorus)
On a mission to cure heart disease,
Distortus-Rex back up, won‚Äôt you please.
Candy wrapper brought us to our knees,
Product placement is mandatory.

(Chant)
Roa-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oh-oar (x4)

(Chorus)
Giant Mosa with four Spinos,
Who‚Äôs the king of the all the dinos?
Swimming T-Rex flippin‚Äô the boat,
River raft with the Delgados.
Quetzalcoatlus singing high notes,
Who‚Äôs the king of the all the dinos?
Hybrid raptors flying so low,
Mutadons attacking your throat.

(Verse 2)
Marooned on this island, can‚Äôt get free,
Move forward and face monstrosities.
Titanosaurus cuddle,
Get samples while they snuggle.
A baby named Dolores,
Hid from Tyrannosaurus.
As big as an F-16,
The Quetz is brutal and mean.
All of the French characters get eaten.

(Pre-chorus)
(Chant)
(Chorus)

(Bridge)
Please, please, open the door,
Don‚Äôt leave me alone with this dinosaur!
Looks more deformed than a xenomorph,
Stacking kills, don‚Äôt make me one more!
I‚Äôll never eat a Snickers again,
Didn‚Äôt mean to endanger my friends. 
Turn the key at the count of three,
Before this abomination eats me‚Ä¶

Aaaaahhhh 

(Chant)
(Chorus)
(Chant)


¬© 2025 Lhugueny

snippet.title: TROLLING SLASHERS with GUEST! [Forsaken]
snippet.description:
*DO NOT HARASS ANYONE IN THIS VIDEO*
Forsaken is a game where survivors work together to stay alive with a killer on the loose. But can I avenge my beloved JASON by punching and parrying SLASHER?

In this video, I use Guest 1337 to parry Slasher as punishment for the bad update. I used one of the new Forsaken Skins in the Forsaken Slasher Update, and for some reason all the Slashers I encountered in this video used the Vanity skin. If you'd like to see how many times I parry and juke killers like a pro, watch until the end!

Don't forget to SUBSCRIBE! We're gonna make it to 200K together!

About Forsaken:
Forsaken is a game with ten survivor characters including Noob, Two Time, Guest 1337, Shedletsky, Elliot, Dusekkar, Builderman, Chance, 007n7, and Taph. There are currently five killer characters as well: SLASHER, C00lkidd, 1x1x1x1, John Doe, and Noli.

#roblox #forsaken #trolling
